This is a brand page for the LIPSATIONAL trademark by CHARLES REVSON INC. 
                                in New York, , 10022.
Write a review about a product or service associated with this LIPSATIONAL trademark.    
                                Or, contact the owner CHARLES REVSON INC. of the LIPSATIONAL trademark by filing a request to communicate with    
                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the LIPSATIONAL trademark.
                           






On Thursday, September 7, 1995,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        LIPSATIONAL by 
                        CHARLES REVSON INC., New York 10022.
                        The USPTO has given the LIPSATIONAL 
                        trademark serial  number of  74726270.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is ABANDONED - NO STATEMENT OF USE FILED.
                        The correspondent listed for LIPSATIONAL is 
                        
                        
                                            Arch M. Ahern of 
                                            Revlon Consumer Products Corporation,  625 Madison Avenue, New York, NY  10022 
                                .
                            The LIPSATIONAL trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Cosmetics and Cleaning Products
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for LIPSATIONAL 
                            is makeup. 
                            





